Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.52,0:00:05.02,Staff,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(280,280)}翻译：goldfish、 Crowst； 校对：無月；歌词：戦闘幽霊；\N定时：SKIP； 繁化：戦闘幽霊； LOGO&特效：面麻； 后期：せんとう；
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.54,0:00:04.38,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\c&H1A6DF2&\pos(1036,1070)}這是我的、願望。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.33,0:00:16.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正因為是今年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.79,0:00:18.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果能夠實現的話就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.99,0:01:53.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.24,0:01:54.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.95,0:01:57.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小川同學 井上同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.16,0:01:59.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.70,0:02:01.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.25,0:02:06.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.00,0:02:11.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有 就是感覺你今天心情比平時還要好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.21,0:02:15.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 被…被你發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.93,0:02:18.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吼吼~真不愧是井上同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.60,0:02:19.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼意思嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.97,0:02:24.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…因為這周週末是七夕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.77,0:02:28.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直期待著這一天來著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.44,0:02:32.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道用什麼表情比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.95,0:02:38.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,七夕是這麼重要的節日麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.99,0:02:44.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是去年好像不是這個樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.91,0:02:45.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.42,0:02:49.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 不好意思稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.25,0:02:52.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 發生什麼事情了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.34,0:02:55.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,井上同學還是老樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.76,0:02:56.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少 少廢話！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.01,0:02:58.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從和她相遇以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.60,0:03:04.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知不覺已經過了一年多了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.15,0:03:11.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.98,0:03:11.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an3}但是果然這個還是接受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,七夕裝飾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.95,0:03:16.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.95,0:03:21.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們家每年都是用媽媽親手做的東西來裝飾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.45,0:03:25.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是搬家的時候不知道被放到哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去年就沒辦法拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.93,0:03:42.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前些天爸爸把它們找出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.22,0:03:45.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慘狀已腦補…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以才心情這麼好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.06,0:03:53.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過 那些是天海媽媽原創的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總感覺好厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加了靈異的特技~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.86,0:04:01.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過 有點在意是什麼樣子的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.12,0:04:02.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 如果方便的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.54,0:04:08.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家週末也一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒 這樣好麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.00,0:04:13.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 媽媽也一定會高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.84,0:04:16.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呀吼~要去要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.01,0:04:18.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,七夕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.88,0:04:23.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說起來 大家都想許什麼願呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.39,0:04:26.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我啊…想讓零花錢變多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.52,0:04:28.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懂得~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.81,0:04:32.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我就…接著殲滅他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.19,0:04:33.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}（不要啊！！！）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.36,0:04:36.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,克服傲嬌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.99,0:04:38.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經決定了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.32,0:04:44.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我 我倒是覺得井上同學現在這個樣子就挺好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以說 我才沒許下什麼克服傲嬌的願望呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.83,0:04:48.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.91,0:04:49.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過 你們想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.00,0:04:53.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不是天海媽媽自製的七夕飾品嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.46,0:04:55.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總覺得會有什麼不可思議的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說不定真的能實現願望之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.76,0:04:59.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能實現哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.88,0:05:02.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,騙人吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.39,0:05:04.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:08.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 在我家每年都實現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什麼！真羨慕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.27,0:05:15.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 想要拍最棒的靈異照片之類的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.11,0:05:18.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我覺得肯定能實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.48,0:05:21.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 和這個人交朋友昵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,僵 殭屍就有點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.38,0:05:36.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,挺厲害的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.63,0:05:40.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然很有派頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位 茶來了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個茶點心是那時候的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果能合大家的口味就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.85,0:05:58.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,厚蛋燒甜甜的很好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 疲勞都被趕走了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 真的很好吃啊 這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是倉鼠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.33,0:06:10.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很高興你們能喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個是 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.16,0:06:15.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.09,0:06:23.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 既然休息好了就開始正戲——許願吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.38,0:06:27.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,值得紀念的第一張就由我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊！我說你也太狡猾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.64,0:06:30.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,（每天都有可愛的女孩子環繞在身邊的幸福後宮生活）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傻不傻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要啊 那是男孩子的夢想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.02,0:06:43.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在這個狀態倒是微妙地實現了那個願望啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.78,0:06:46.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然跟可愛和幸福完全沒有茉系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.03,0:06:50.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個對別人許的願也會實現嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.70,0:06:51.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.50,0:06:59.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在想如果這樣寫的話有點像給別人姻緣一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,憤怒產生的靈異現象？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.31,0:07:14.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對…對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.52,0:07:17.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道你們原來這麼不願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.27,0:07:19.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘛 畢竟也算是死對頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.36,0:07:20.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.57,0:07:26.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能實現願望是連這種惡作劇也會實現的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.28,0:07:32.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這是想寫誰的名字啊 嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.49,0:07:36.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 是誰和誰呢~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然馬上就開始玩上了 何等厚顏無恥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正你們都是悶葫蘆 相配的很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說什麼？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.43,0:07:52.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是所謂關繫好到可以吵架…嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在就是機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.35,0:08:00.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼哼哼哼哼 老夫的願望只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.23,0:08:05.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超薄布料的 裙底走光！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貓爪真是難用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.24,0:08:13.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貓先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.87,0:08:16.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,仔細想想的話很煩惱要寫什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.16,0:08:20.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大半的願望都是自己努力就能實現的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.08,0:08:23.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比如零花錢啊 成績啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,殲滅也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.42,0:08:26.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}（大哥!）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說起來 天海你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,許了什麼願呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.97,0:08:35.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒 沒什麼 是非常普通的事哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看起來一點都不普通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.35,0:08:39.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.32,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\frz270\pos(520,496)}希望能交到很多朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.98,0:08:46.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.57,0:08:50.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 雖然很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.07,0:08:57.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我從小除了幽靈以外和別的都沒什麼緣分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 就沒有掛上去的必要了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.92,0:09:06.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了 你們也是 趕緊寫好願望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.63,0:09:10.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說 願望什麼的寫個家宅平安之類的不就行了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.22,0:09:14.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我的願望就是希望他能再動起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.39,0:09:14.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是不會放棄後宮的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.06,0:09:20.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,內褲~內褲~內褲~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.10,0:09:26.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 喔 什麼啊 不是還有一張嗎~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.28,0:09:33.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不把那一張掛上去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.00,0:09:43.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了 現在已經足夠幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.33,0:09:48.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,許這種願只是任性而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也快來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.93,0:09:54.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.35,0:10:01.85,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\frz270\pos(922,634)}我想見到媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.32,0:10:11.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想見到媽媽啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.49,0:10:14.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是身為孩子理所當然的願望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.11,0:10:18.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把這樣理所當然之事當做是任性的天海殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.12,0:10:20.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓在下感到很心酸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那張髒兮兮的紙簽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是從什麼時候開始就寫好的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.79,0:10:28.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,響妹子簡直小氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.84,0:10:31.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對別人媽媽的事情插嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,輪到自己了就沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓人超火大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.43,0:10:36.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海的媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.01,0:10:37.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夕陽殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.55,0:10:42.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為何一次都不回到天海殿下的身邊昵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.81,0:10:46.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或許並不是不想回來 而是無法回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.48,0:10:47.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像我一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被束縛在某個地萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.19,0:10:50.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,束縛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.78,0:10:55.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吶 之前我不是依附在響妹子身上過麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.75,0:11:04.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到了什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.79,0:11:05.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.29,0:11:10.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但總感覺很溫暖很溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.67,0:11:11.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.18,0:11:21.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看什麼看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.35,0:11:22.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這個禿頭锃亮武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.93,0:11:24.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太不講理了是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之 確實有留下那種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.19,0:11:30.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道那就是響妹子的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.06,0:11:31.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然是這樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.32,0:11:35.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過如果是這樣的話 為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.36,0:11:37.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 如果真是這樣的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.95,0:11:38.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到此為止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還什麼都沒說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們本來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.04,0:11:46.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所謂生者 就是擁有愛的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.37,0:11:51.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在觸碰到生者強烈而耀眼的生命之淵時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.88,0:11:52.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會發生什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們根本無法預料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.42,0:11:58.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果好好聽從說教的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還當什麼小太妹~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣真的好麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.72,0:12:05.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可別小看小太妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.14,0:12:09.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是想把欠的人情還了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.52,0:12:17.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 這就是傲嬌是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海殿下 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是…響妹子的記憶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.89,0:12:43.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這一帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.01,0:12:46.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應當是天海殿下和咱們相遇之前的記憶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從以前就一點沒變啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.73,0:12:51.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才的是！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.06,0:12:53.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.86,0:12:54.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這…多麼溫暖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.13,0:13:15.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是什麼啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.88,0:13:17.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,牽牛花？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 比起這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.18,0:13:25.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冒昧造訪 請您原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.14,0:13:27.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,閣下莫非是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歡迎到訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an7\fs45\3c&H000000&}注：原文「おいでませ」是日本山口县的方言，\N相当于「ようこそいらつしやいました」即“欢\N迎光临”的意思。与餐馆或商店里店员对顾客\N使用的「いらつしやいませ」不同，这句一般\N是对拜访自家的客人说的。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.94,0:13:39.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒…誒！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(538,94)}歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是響的母親夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那孩子的朋友能來到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.91,0:13:48.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是多麼令人開心的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.45,0:13:50.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就是代答武士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常感謝你一直以來守護著響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是有點太瘦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要挑食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海苔雞蛋之外的貢品也要好好全吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.05,0:14:04.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,記住了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.39,0:14:06.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謹…謹記是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這邊這位非常可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.43,0:14:12.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對對~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個時候很流行這樣的款式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.19,0:14:17.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還想著至少要穿一次昵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是媽媽不允許…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.48,0:14:21.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不覺得很過分麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.03,0:14:21.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,o(>3<)o
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.49,0:14:27.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…感覺和服很適合您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.53,0:14:29.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是溫柔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.41,0:14:33.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我能摸摸這個薄襪麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.71,0:14:34.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.46,0:14:35.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好長~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.46,0:14:39.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等…您在搞什麼啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們可不是來玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明 明明就在這麼近的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼就不去見響妹子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.68,0:14:52.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海殿下現在也在祈願能夠見到您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.85,0:14:55.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去見見她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.31,0:14:58.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,響妹子一直都這樣祈求著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.11,0:15:06.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道 我一直都從這裡看著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.20,0:15:11.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.97,0:15:26.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夕陽殿下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.55,0:15:37.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個孩子需要我一直在這裡守護著她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.98,0:15:43.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她是我們的非常重要的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重要的…什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.41,0:15:50.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那種事無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.74,0:15:53.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不想去見見響妹子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,響妹子的事無關緊要嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.79,0:16:02.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連像我這樣的女兒也一直掛念著的 不就是媽媽嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.71,0:16:04.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.97,0:16:09.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.64,0:16:14.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種事對一個母親來說不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.98,0:16:21.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很想見她哦 非常地想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.90,0:16:30.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我一次都沒能擁抱過她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.24,0:16:39.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是不可以 這裡必須要有我的力量來滋潤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:42.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是一會兒怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.92,0:16:48.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是一會兒 在下代替夕陽殿下留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.72,0:16:52.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這期間能不能去見見天海殿下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我 我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們有這份心意我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.68,0:16:58.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.31,0:17:01.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有兩個人的話是沒辦法代替我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.06,0:17:06.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 這樣如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.91,0:17:16.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼你們會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.95,0:17:19.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多管閒事的傢伙哪裡都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.25,0:17:24.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「估計你們肯定不會聽我說的話」他這麼說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咱也是 雖然有點辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但還是來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.51,0:17:34.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 不管是誰都一副愛管事的大閒人的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位 感激不盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.43,0:17:40.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙的心裡是不需要雨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.68,0:17:44.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要小天海能夠快樂 咱就很高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.27,0:17:49.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,優心忡忡的小姐的走光 就算看到了也覺得不滿足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.99,0:17:54.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也想讓姐姐一直陪我玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.54,0:18:03.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個孩子 就算是以我的力量而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,保護這個孩子的負擔也並不算小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.09,0:18:07.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.38,0:18:12.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給大家太多的負擔之後結果會怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.59,0:18:14.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰都不知道的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.47,0:18:17.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使這樣也無所謂是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.14,0:18:18.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,武士先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.76,0:18:22.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要是為了讓我敞開心靈的天海殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就什麼都不需要害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.57,0:18:35.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,響 這就是你的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.29,0:18:41.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,響 響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.34,0:18:57.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.47,0:19:02.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,媽…媽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.78,0:19:20.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.78,0:19:21.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,初次見面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.33,0:19:28.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 雖然我一直有看到照片 這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長大了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.92,0:19:35.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為爸爸很珍愛地撫養著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.56,0:19:50.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起哦 明明我知道你一直都在許這個願…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.11,0:19:54.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…沒 沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.32,0:19:58.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因 因為一直都有爸爸陪著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幽靈的各位也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.82,0:20:01.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還 還有朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.66,0:20:05.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.21,0:20:12.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能讓我抱抱嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.81,0:20:27.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.08,0:20:52.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夕陽…小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.38,0:20:58.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.74,0:21:21.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.83,0:21:33.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,…不是夢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.46,0:21:38.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 那個 媽媽來看我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.46,0:21:41.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,代答武士先生 小太妹小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.84,0:21:46.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那個 其他的各位…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.31,0:21:54.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有沒有人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.61,0:21:57.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果能聽到我的聲音的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.02,0:22:00.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請讓我看一看你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.74,0:22:02.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我聽一聽聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.91,0:22:05.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.95,0:22:07.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.29,0:23:43.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本來想著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.55,0:23:45.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「托天海靈感消失的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.51,0:23:47.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每天過得真是和平啊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.63,0:23:49.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是這忍受不了的感覺是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.93,0:23:52.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,具實現在也還是怕幽靈怕得不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.10,0:23:55.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有點害怕天海的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.23,0:23:58.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是一看到她那樣的表情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.60,0:24:02.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 真是的 好頭大！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.27,0:24:05.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下回RE一KAN！「大家是、緊密相連的。」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.40,0:24:08.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海 給我稍微有點表情啊！

